  <refsect1>
    <title>Description</title>

<para>
<application>gephex-gui</application>
is the graphical frontend of the interactive video effect system GePhex.
You have to start the
 <citerefentry> <refentrytitle>gephex-engine</refentrytitle> <manvolnum>1</manvolnum> </citerefentry>
and after that you can start the gui.
</para>

<para>The projects main intent is to create a framework that allows videojockeys to design complex realtime video effects. The user can influence parameters 
and data flow with interactive controls like joysticks or mididevices.</para>
  </refsect1>

